title: Elvis Presley - St Louis blues (2013)
description:
Recorded live at Kiel Auditorium
March 22 1976, St. Louis, MO



Tracklisting

2001 Theme / C C Rider / I Got A Woman - Amen / Love Me / Let Me Be There (+ reprise) / You Gave Me A Mountain / Steamroller Blues / All Shook Up / Teddy Bear - Dont Be Cruel / Heartbreak Hotel / Love Me Tender / Polk Salad Annie / Band Introductions / Whatd I Say ( featuring James Burton ) / Drum Solo ( featuring Larry Londin ) / Bass Solo ( featuring Jerry Scheff ) / Piano Solo ( featuring Shane Keister ) / Electric Piano Solo ( featuring David Briggs ) / School Day / And I Love You So / Hurt / Hound Dog / America The Beautiful / Funny How Time Slips Away / Cant Help Falling In Love / Closing Vamp

Bonus Tracks

Love Me / You Gave Me A Mountain / Let Me Be There (+reprise) / Steamroller Blues / All Shook Up / Teddy Bear - Dont Be Cruel / Heartbreak Hotel / Love Me Tender / Polk Salad Annie (+ false start)

Recorded live in Johnson City, TN. March 19, 1976
Recording: Audience

Label: EP Collector EPC 2013-01 (Released 2013)
